commonMistakes.correction:
**Forgetting dependency array**:
   ```jsx
   // WRONG! Runs after EVERY render
   useEffect(() => {
     fetchData();  // Infinite loop if it updates state!
   });

   // CORRECT!
   useEffect(() => {
     fetchData();
   }, []);  // Run once on mount
   ```

**Using async directly in useEffect**:
   ```jsx
   // WRONG!
   useEffect(async () => {  // Can't make effect async!
     const data = await fetch('/api/users');
   }, []);

   // CORRECT!
   useEffect(() => {
     async function fetchData() {
       const data = await fetch('/api/users');
     }
     fetchData();
   }, []);
   ```
